![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578252254189-XGS9PCZDGO3TXCMDNI1V/Episode73.jpg?format=original)

The dust has settled, and the smoke has cleared, and here we stand as survivors of Avengers Endgame. With many of us still dealing with the emotional effects of the film, less than a week from its release, ComicBook Clique has got your back with our Endgame Therapy Session! It's the action packed review you have been waiting for, about one of the biggest films of our generation, brought to you by your loyal host of Major Issues. Put down your mead, pick up your hammer and remember we love you 3000 in our most anticipated episode yet!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

